nodes.text: This swoop race was held annually in Tasjon, a city on the planet of Corulag, in the waning years of the Galactic Republic. In 22 BBY, it was won by Ignar Ominaz.

This race was mentioned in an issue of the HoloNet News feed (2002), Volume 531, Issue 54. The article that referenced the race, titled "Ominaz Keeps Top Ranking," was written by Pablo Hidalgo and Paul Ens.
